metadata.title: K40 K4018FME 18ft Super Mini-8 CB Antenna Cable with Removable FME Connector, Black
features: 95% shielded design protects from loss of signal for increased performance
Molded ends for moisture, dust, and corrosion protection
description: This 18 foot super mini-8 CB antenna cable has a removable FME style connector. For more custom installation, a smaller hole will need to be drilled. 95% shielded design protects from loss of signal for increased performance. Molded ends protect from moisture, dust, and corrosion.
